CCA: CPC * 1/CR


2$ per click, 50% of people sign up, each signup is 2 * 1/0.5

$2 per click, x% of people sign up, each signup is 

LTV: $500


2 * (1/x) = 500
1/x = 250
1 = 250 * x
1/250 = x

>0.4 % of clicks to paying users is the goal to make running display ads profitable (assuming that life time REVENUE of customer is $500.)

Note: at this rate, it would take 20 days to generate 250 clicks (limited by budget,) and would cost $500.



